      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "TRAINSET (64 pairs from existing\nprompts + DB tasks)\n         ↓\nMETRIC (validator + section/file/\nlength similarity)\n         ↓\nOPTIMIZER\n• BootstrapFewShot ($1, ~3min)\n• MIPROv2 ($5-50, longer)\n         ↓\nCOMPILED PROGRAM\n   prompt_generator/compiled/\n   agent_bootstrap.json\n         ↓\n  Loaded by Generator at runtime",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "TRAINSET (64 pairs from existing\nprompts + DB tasks)\n         ↓\nMETRIC (validator + section/file/\nlength similarity)\n         ↓\nOPTIMIZER\n• BootstrapFewShot ($1, ~3min)\n• MIPROv2 ($5-50, longer)\n         ↓\nCOMPILED PROGRAM\n   prompt_generator/compiled/\n   agent_bootstrap.json\n         ↓\n  Loaded by Generator at runtime",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
