      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Legend:  GREEN = pure Python (deterministic)   ORANGE = LLM call (DSPy ChainOfThought)\n         PURPLE = LLM verifier (DSPy ChainOfThought)   RED diamond = decision\n         YELLOW dashed = compilation pipeline (one-time, separate from runtime flow)\n         RED dashed arrow = refinement feedback loop (verifier feedback re-enters generator)",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Legend:  GREEN = pure Python (deterministic)   ORANGE = LLM call (DSPy ChainOfThought)\n         PURPLE = LLM verifier (DSPy ChainOfThought)   RED diamond = decision\n         YELLOW dashed = compilation pipeline (one-time, separate from runtime flow)\n         RED dashed arrow = refinement feedback loop (verifier feedback re-enters generator)",
